\c 17
\s Dhavhidhi anouraya Goriati
\p
\v 1 Lvino vaHisitia vakakoka hondo dzavo kuzorwa, vakaungana
\p paSoko raiva raJudha, vakavaka misasa yavo pakati peSoko naAzeka paEfesidamimi.
\v 2 Sauro navarume vaIsiraeri vakaunganawo, vakavaka misasa yavo pamu‑
\p pata weEra, vakagadzira hondo kuzorwa navaFirisitia.
\v 3 VaFirisitia vakanga vamire pagomo kuno rumwe rutivi, navaisiraeri vakanga vamire pagomo kuno rumwe rutivi; mupata wakanga uri pakati pavo.
\p
\v 4 Zvino kumisasa yavaFirisitia kwakabuda mhare, yainzi Goriati weGati; kureba kwake kwakanga kuna makubhiti matanhatu uye sapanosvika minwe.
\v 5 Wakanga ane ngoani yendarira pamusoro wake, uye wakanga akafuka nguo dzokurwa dzamabape endarira, nguo dzokurwa dzamabape endarira dzakasvika mashekeri ane zviuru zvishanu zvendarira pakurema kwadzo.
\v 6 Wakanga ane zvidzitiro zvamakumbo zvendarira, nemharu yendarira pakati pamafudzi ake.
\p
\v 7 Rwiriko rwepfumo rake rwakanga rwakafanana nedanda romuruki; nechese yepfumo rake yakasvika mashekeri ana mazana matanhatu amatare pakurema kwayo; uye mubati wenhowo yake waifamba mberi kwake.
\v 8 Akamira, akadanidzira kuhondo dzavaIsiraeri, akati kwavari, "Mabudireiko muchigadzira hondo yenyu? Ini handizi muFirisitia, nemi varanda vaSauro here? Imi muzvitsaurire murume, aburukire kuno kwandiri.
\v 9 Kana akagona kurwa neni, akandiuraya, isu tichava varanda venyu; asi kana ini ndikamukunda, ndikamuuraya, imi muchava varanda vedu, muchatibatira."
\v 10 MuFirisitia akati, "Nhasi ndinoshoora hondo dzavaIsiraeri, ndipei munhu, tirwe."
\v 11 Zvino Sauro navaIsiraeri vose vakati vachinzwa mashoko awa
\s sitia, vakavhunduka, vakatya kwazvo.
\p
\v 12 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakanga ari mwanakomana womuEfurata weBheterehemujudha, wainzi Jese; iye wakanga ana vanakomana vasere, asi munhu uyu wakanga ava mutana pamazuva aSauro, akwegura pakati pavarume.
\v 13 Vanakomana vatatu vakuru vaJese vakanga vaenda naSauro kundorwa; zvino mazita avana vake vatatu, vakanga vaenda kundorwa, akanga ari, Eriabhu wedangwe, tevere Abhinadhabhu, wechitatu Shama.
\p
\v 14 Dhavhidhi wakanga ari muduku kuna vose; vaiwu vatatu vakanga v aenda naSauro.
\v 15 Zvino Dhavhidhi waisienda kuna Sauro, achidzoka kuzofudza makwai ababa vake paBheterehemu.
\v 16 MuFirisitia waiswedera mangwana namadeko, akamirapo mazuva ana makumi mana.
\p
\v 17 Zvino Jese akati kuna Dhavhidhi mwanakomana wake, "Chindopa vakuru vako imwe yezviyo izvi zvakakangwa, nezvingwa zvine gumi, ukurumidze kuzviisa kumisasa kuvakuru vako;
\v 18 asi mapundu awa omukaka wakafa ane gumi uise kumukuru wechuru chavo, ugotarira kuti vakuru vako vakadiniko, ndokutora kwavari chokuwonerapo."
\v 19 Zvino Sauro, naivo navarume vose vaIsiraeri vakanga vari pamupata weEra vachirwa navaFirisitia.
\p
\v 20 Dhavhidhi akamuka mangwanani, akasiya makwai ake kumufudzi, akatora nhumbi, akaenda kwaakanga arairwa naJese; akasvika pakanga pakarundwa ngoro, varwi vobuda vachiridza mhere kundorwa.
\v 21 VaIsiraeri navaFirisitia vakazvigadzira kurwa, hondo dzakatarisana.
\v 22 Dhavhidhi akasiya nhumbi dzake pamaoko omutariri wenhumbi, akamhanyira kuhondo, akasvika akakwazisa vakuru vake.
\v 23 Zvino wakati achataura navo, iya mhare ikabuda kuhondo yavaFirisitia, iye muFirisitia weGati, wainzi Goriati, akataura mashoko aaisitaura, Dhavhidhi akaanzwa.
\v 24 Zvino varume vose vaIsiraeri vakati vachiona murume uyu, vakamutiza, vakatya kwazvo.
\v 25 Varume vaIsiraeri vakati, "Maona here murume uyo, wakwira? Zvirokwazvo wakwira kuzoshoora Isiraeri; munhu unomuuraya, mambo uchamufumisa nefuma zhinji, nokumupawo mwanasikana wake, nokusunungura imba yababa vake munaIsiraeri."
\p
\v 26 Zvino Dhavhidhi akataura navarume vakanga vamire naye, akati, "Munhu,• unouraya muFirisitia uyu, akabvisa kushoorwa kwavaIsiraeri uchapiweiko? Nokuti muFirisitia uyu usinokudzingiswa ndianiko, unoshoora hondo dzaMwari mupenyu?"
\v 27 Vanhu vakamupindura saizvozvo, vakati, "Munhu, unomuuraya, uchapiwa chokuti nechokuti."
\p
\v 28 Zvino Eriabhu mukoma wake mukuru akanzwa achitaura navarume avo, Eriabhu akatsamwira Dhavhidhi, akati, "Waburukireiko pano iwe? Makwai aya mashoma waasiya naniko murenje? Ndinoziva manyawi ako, nokuipa kwo‑
\s mwoyo wako, nok.Naburuka kuzoona
\s hondo."
\p
\v 29 Dhavhidhi akati, "Zvino ndadiniko hangu? Handina kungobvunza hangu here?"
\p
\v 30 Akatendeukirazve kunomumwe, akataurazve saizvozvo; vanhu vakamupindurazve saizvozvo.
\p
\v 31 Zvino vakati vanzwa mashoko akataurwa naDhavhidhi, vakaarondedzera kuna Sauro; akatuma munhu kuzomudana.
\v 32 Dhavhidhi akati kuna Sauro, "Ngakurege kuva nomunhu unopera mwoyo nokuda kwake; muranda wenyu uchaenda kundorwa nomuFirisitia uyo."
\p
\v 33 Sauro akati kuna Dhavhidhi, "Haungagoni kundorwa nomuFirisitia uyo, nokuti uchiri mukomana, asi iye murume murwi kubva pauduku hwake."
\p
\v 34 Dhavhidhi akati kuna Sauro, "Muranda wenyu waifudza makwai ababa vake; zvino kana shumba ikasvika, kana bere, kuzotora gwayana paboka,
\v 35 ndaibuda, ndikaitevera, ndikaiuraya, ndikaiwira pamuromo wayo; kana ichinge ikandimukira, ndaibata ndebvu dzayo, ndokuibaya nokuiuraya."
\v 36 Muranda wenyu akazviuraya zvose, kunyangwe shumba kunyangwe bere; muFirisitia uyu usinokudzingiswa uchafanana nechimwe chazvo, nokuti wakashora hondo dzaMwari mupenyu.
\v 37 Dhavhidhi akati, "Jehovha wakandirwira pagumbo reshumba negumbo rebere, iye uchandirwirawo paruoko rwomuFirisitia uyu." Ipapo Sauro akati kuna Dhavhidhi, "Enda hako, Jehovha uchava newe."
\v 38 Sauro akafukidza Dhavhidhi nguo dzake, akadzika ngoani yendarira pamusoro wake, akamufukidza nguo dzokurwa dzamabape endarira.
\v 39 Zvino Dhavhidhi akasungira munondo wake pamusoro penguo dzake, akaidza kufamba; nokuti wakanga asina kumboidza izvozvo. Dhavhidhi akati kuna Sauro, "Handigoni kufamba nadzo, nokuti handina kumbodziidza." Dhavhidhi akadzibvisa.
\v 40 Akabata tsvimbo muruoko rwake, akazvitsaurira hurungudo shanu parukova, akadziisa muhombodo yake yomufudzi, yaakanga anayo, imo munhava yake; chifuramabwe chake chakanga chiri muruoko rwake; akaswedera kumuFirisitia.
\p
\v 41 MuFirisitia akauya, akaswedera kuna Dhavhidhi; munhu wakanga akabata nhovo yake akamutungamirira.
\v 42 Zvino muFirisitia wakati achitarira, akaona Dhavhidhi, akamuzvidza; nokuti wakanga achiri mukomana hake, mutsvuku, ane chiso chakanaka.
\v 43 MuFirisitia akati kuna Dhavhidhi, "Ndiri imbwa
